<h1 style="text-align:center;">Jesus' Messages<br>Delivered by Rev. Brandon Olivares</h1>

<p>I started to receive Jesus' messages on March 21, 2011. Since then, they have been a constant source of spiritual teaching and solace for many people. He brings His spiritual message of light and love to the modern time, and dispels many of the perversions that have been introduced to His message over the millennia. Jesus' messages revive the spirit of early Christian spirituality that has been diluted over time. He emphasizes love and forgiveness over judgment and condemnation, and shows us the way back to God by allowing the light of Christ to shine in and through us always.</p>

<p style="border: 1px solid #000066">Have these messages had an impact on you, or you just want to share your own experience with Jesus and His messages?<br>
