<p>Jesus started appearing to me in late February, 2011, but I had no idea what His plans were for me then. He had warned me even as far back as July, 2010, that my path would be a very unique one, and that He would be guiding me down that path Himself. How true that was!</p>

<p>As He appeared to me more frequently, my personal beliefs began to become altered without me even realizing it. I started to look to Him more and more, and realized that I was supposed to teach and to heal like He did. Soon, on March 20, He revealed to me that I was to begin to deliver His spiritual teachings every day.</p>

<p>These messages are listed below in reverse chronological order, from the most recent message at the top. I sincerely hope that you enjoy them, and that they have a beneficial effect in your life. Simply read them with an open mind, even if you don't agree with everything at first. Allow Christ's light to penetrate your being, regardless of what your beliefs are, and you will begin to be transformed by His messages within your daily life.</p>

